System Test Plan

Module Testing
++++++++++++++++++
	Visit each module and preform the Makefile runtest.

CS1 Testing
++++++++++++++++++
	Use Makefile to execute KWIC with different noise word files and input files. Then call diff and the actual output and the expected output.
	
	Test 1: Input from stdin
	Test 2: Command line argument
	Test 3: 2 input files from command line argument
	Test 4: Use default noisewords
	Test 5: Use a specified noisewords file
	Test 6: Use environment variables to specifiy noisewords file
	
	

